			<conclusion>
				<p>
					We've investigated the three main cube moves: the Three Corner Tango (which cycles the position of three corners on the front face), the Three Edge Tango (which cycles the position of three edges on the up face), and the Corner Bulldog (which reorients two corners at opposite ends of the Cube).
